There was an automatic sniper so I climbed the building, broke the computer and took the rifle. Then, I went on killing enemies but it wasn't like a game. Enemies aren't red dots, they just wear different clothing. Also, the rifle's scope was in heat detection.

I also jumped off the building with a parachute after some guys noticed me and came up the building.
